	 mso 9]><xml>\n<o:shapelayout v:ext="edit">\n<o:idmap v:ext="edit" data="1
	" />\n</o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]--></head><body lang=EN-US link="#467
	886" vlink="#96607D" style='tab-interval:.5in\;word-wrap:break-word'><div 
	class=WordSection1><p class=MsoNormal>Kube &amp\; Tell is a live\, communi
	ty-driven podcast for Kubernetes practitioners who'd rather show than tell
	. Expect hands-on walkthroughs\, deep technical dives\, and candid convers
	ations spanning AKS\, upstream Kubernetes\, self-hosted clusters\, and the
	 wider cloud-native ecosystem.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>Best of al
	l\, we record it live. So as the audience\, you can bring in your question
	s\, your hot takes\, and your war stories. The mic is open.<o:p></o:p></p>
	<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><b>Agenda and 
	Join Link:</b>&nbsp\;<a href="https://aka.ms/aks/communitycalls" target="_
	blank">https://aka.ms/aks/communitycalls</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNor
	mal><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></p></div></body></html>
